All code, documentation, and simulation results in this repository
are personal learning output for educational and research purposes only.
Use in production, commercial products, or safety-critical systems
is strongly discouraged.

## 硬件安全声明 / Hardware Safety

FPGA / 数字电路代码的错误可能导致：
- 时序违例引起系统不稳定
- 过流 / 过热导致硬件物理损坏
- 数据丢失或损坏

使用者自行承担全部风险。作者不对因使用本代码造成的任何
硬件损坏、数据丢失、财产损失负责。

Errors in FPGA/digital circuit code may cause system instability,
physical hardware damage, or data loss. Use entirely at your own risk.
The author assumes no liability for any damages.

